\begin_layout Corollary
Let 
\begin_inset Formula $M$
\end_inset

 be a surface without focal points and 
\begin_inset Formula $\vphi$
\end_inset

 is a constant function.
 Then there exists a unique equilibrium 
\begin_inset Formula $\mu_{\vphi}$
\end_inset

 for 
\begin_inset Formula $\vphi$
\end_inset

.
 Moreover 
\begin_inset Formula $\mu_{\vphi}$
\end_inset

 is Bernoulli.
 
\end_layout

